description: She hates you, she loves you, we love her! Our OTP is hanging out with us this week...Miss Olivia O'Brien and Mr. Don Julio! What's Olivia's problem with Zane? Is tequila her most loyal relationship? Cap or no cap? These very important questions are all answered right here. We're addicted to Olivia's endless wild stories, like the time she got Drake addicted to... well, you'll hear about it. Get your booty shakin jeans on, and let's party! xoxo
